                cp_events = cfg.get("cp_events")

                    cp_events_enable = cp_events.get("enable")
                else:
                    cp_events_enable = False
                dp_events = cfg.get("dp_events")

                    rx_rate_threshold = dp_events.get("rx_rate_threshold")
